{"tid":931492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"審議一地兩檢爆衝突保安稱受傷 林卓廷尹兆堅遭預約拘捕","createTime":"2018-12-07T05:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T08:33:14.000Z","uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c754ee3917091afba908843b1294c784a120fd75","tid":931492,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181207&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59002739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181207%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59002739&d=KSHrbrcZAjs90lyxCGdwe9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f4c47922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181207%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59002739&h=89423fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181207&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59002739</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府今年6月在立法會硬推西九高鐵站《廣深港高鐵(一地兩檢)條例草案》，民主派在表決前夕用盡規程力阻惡法通過，6月13日議會期間更出現大混亂，導致有保安員、民主黨議員林卓廷及尹兆堅同告受傷送院。林卓廷及尹兆堅今日接獲警方通知，將就兩人當日的行為進行預約拘捕及提出檢控。《蘋果》向尹查詢，他證實被警方預約捕，詳情稍後交代。<br />\n<br />\n據知，二人將於內會後見無綫新聞引述消息指，兩人涉及普通襲擊，及妨礙正執行職務的立法會人員。當日立法會二讀通過「一地兩檢」條例草案，多名民主派議員抗議主席梁君彥不准發言時被趕離場，事後林卓廷、尹兆堅及立法會兩名保安報稱受傷，警方曾到大樓調查。<br />\n<br />\n=========<br />\n乜實Q都係立法會人員咩？"},{"pid":"f86ac0be6bcc63239758514fa3155bf4d13e8cc5","tid":931492,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"無人理？"},{"pid":"43647ebbc2e9e78d8af4575c77cec99714833048","tid":931492,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"議員妨礙保安執行職務？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f741d48fe22a4af56c4f5fd43471b773ae839289","tid":931492,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43647ebbc2e9e78d8af4575c77cec9